<div class="" style="font-size:110%;">The works of <strong class="selflink">Karl Marx</strong> and <a href="Friedrich_Engels" title="Friedrich Engels">Friedrich Engels</a></div>
</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px;">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style=";;">Marx</th>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd hlist">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<ul>
<li><i><a href="Scorpion_and_Felix" title="Scorpion and Felix">Scorpion and Felix</a></i> (1837)</li>
<li><i><a href="Critique_of_Hegel's_Philosophy_of_Right" title="Critique of Hegel's Philosophy of Right">Critique of Hegel's Philosophy of Right</a></i> (1843)</li>
<li><i><a href="On_the_Jewish_Question" title="On the Jewish Question">On the Jewish Question</a></i> (1843)</li>
<li><i><a href="Notes_on_James_Mill" title="Notes on James Mill">Notes on James Mill</a></i> (1844)</li>
<li><i><a href="Economic_and_Philosophic_Manuscripts_of_1844" title="Economic and Philosophic Manuscripts of 1844">Economic and Philosophic Manuscripts of 1844</a></i> (1844, published in 1927)</li>
<li><i><a href="Theses_on_Feuerbach" title="Theses on Feuerbach">Theses on Feuerbach</a></i> (1845, published in 1888)</li>
<li><i><a href="The_Poverty_of_Philosophy" title="The Poverty of Philosophy">The Poverty of Philosophy</a></i> (1847)</li>
<li><i><a href="Wage-Labor_and_Capital" title="Wage-Labor and Capital" class="mw-redirect">Wage-Labor and Capital</a></i> (1847)</li>
<li><i><a href="../../w/index-title=The_Class_Struggles_in_France,_1848%E2%80%931850&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="The Class Struggles in France, 1848–1850 (page does not exist)">The Class Struggles in France, 1848–1850</a></i> (1850)</li>
<li><i><a href="The_Eighteenth_Brumaire_of_Louis_Napoleon" title="The Eighteenth Brumaire of Louis Napoleon">The Eighteenth Brumaire of Louis Napoleon</a></i> (1852)</li>
<li><i><a href="Grundrisse" title="Grundrisse">Grundrisse</a></i> (1857, published in 1939)</li>
<li><i><a href="A_Contribution_to_the_Critique_of_Political_Economy" title="A Contribution to the Critique of Political Economy">A Contribution to the Critique of Political Economy</a></i> (1859)</li>
<li><i><a href="Theories_of_Surplus_Value" title="Theories of Surplus Value">Theories of Surplus Value</a></i>, 3 volumes (1862)</li>
